                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Germano <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>veter</abbr><ex>ano</ex></expan> ex <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urione</ex></expan> et <lb n="3"/>Cassiae Valentin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>eius et Publiis Aeliis <lb n="5"/>Sabiniano et Germano <lb n="6"/>dec&amp;lt;c=G&amp;gt;(urionibus) <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">II(viris)</supplied> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> coloniae <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ureliae</ex></expan> &amp;lt;O=Q&amp;gt;vil&amp;lt;ei=AV&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>ensi</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> a militiis <lb n="8"/>et &amp;lt;Ael=P&amp;gt;(iae) Valentinae sor<lb break="no" n="9"/>ori e&amp;lt;g=Q&amp;gt;(regiae) <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>uellae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Ae&amp;lt;li=T&amp;gt;us <lb n="10"/>Rufin<surplus>i</surplus>us <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> et <lb n="11"/>IIvir &amp;lt;<expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan>=L&amp;gt; <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> A&amp;lt;e&amp;gt;<abbr>l</abbr> <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>Cetiens</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/>perfici <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich überliefert. Lesungsvorschlag weitgehend nach Alföldy und Wedenig. Datierung: nicht vor 211 n. Chr., da Ovilava wahrscheinlich unter Caracalla den Status einer colonia erhielt.</p>
